text_264596390.text:
Model Q & Model Z

The Model Q is our premium automobile. It has the best safety and performance characteristics of any car on the market.

The Model Z is our economy variant for drivers that want the authentic AUTO experience at an affordable price. It is not as advanced as the Model Q, but it is just as safe.

text_1737882774.text:
3 - 5 Weeks

New Model Q cars in inventory will be delivered in the US in no more than 5 weeks. Custom orders may take additional time.

text_665231219.text:
Safety

  • Sensor-controlled automatic braking and steering
  • Surround Airbag System
  • Traction control and electronic stability

Convenience

  • GPS navigation through driver display
  • 4G wireless connection
  • Push-button start
  • Gesture-activated controls
  • Tri-folding seats

Standard Features

  • Illuminated digital displays
  • Adjustable heating and air conditioning
  • 5-way adjustable front seats
  • AM/FM/Satellite Radio
  • Phone charging station

Premium Options

  • Heated seats and steering wheel
  • Electronic Sun/Moon Roof
  • Solar charging panels
  • Upgraded surround-sound entertainment system
  • All-leather interior upholstery
  • Automatic windshield wiper/defroster system

Warranty

  • 5 year, 60,000 mile limited vehicle warranty
  • 10 year, 100,000 mile power system warranty (Standard)
  • 15 year, 1,500,000 mile power system warranty (Optional)
